<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../090/417090.xml">
Drama Desk Award</link></award>
 for Outstanding One-Person Show. She was nominated for two <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../741/54741.xml">
Tony Awards</link> in 1994 for <it>Twilight</it>. One for Best Actress and another for Best Play. The play won her a <award wordnetid="106696483" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../090/417090.xml">
Drama Desk Award</link></award>
